title: Kids Playground at 313@somerset Sky Terrace
blurb: Enjoy the Kids playground at Sky Terrace!
description: The Sky Terrace at 313@somerset features a dedicated kids' playground, providing a fun and safe environment for children to play and explore. Parents can relax while kids enjoy the play structures. The playground is designed for young children and offers a variety of activities to keep them entertained. It's a great place for families to spend time together while shopping or dining at 313@somerset. The playground is located on the Sky Terrace, offering a pleasant outdoor setting for families.
